Package: sparklyr.nested
Title: A Sparklyr Extension for Nested Data
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matt", "Pollock", email = "mpollock@mitre.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(family = "The MITRE Corporation", role = c("cph"))
    )
Maintainer: Matt Pollock <mpollock@mitre.org>
Description: A sparklyr extension adding the capability to work easily with nested data using
